header.gameNote: NAISMITH MEMORIAL HALL OF FAME TIP-OFF - CAMPUS GAME

videos.description: Marist is having a rough go of it in the first half against No. 1 Duke. Khallid Hart's 3-point attempt gets wedged against the rim, and on the next possession, Isaiah Lamb's shot gets blocked by Duke's Amile Jefferson, wedging against the rim.
videos.headline: Marist gets the ball stuck on back-to-back possessions
Duke put-back dunk extends their lead to 35

videos.description: Duke's Matt Jones makes an easy pick of a Marist pass and takes it the other way for a strong left-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Matt Jones swipes and slams for Duke

videos.description: 2H (9:47) DUKE Javin DeLaurier made Dunk. Assisted by Frank Jackson.
videos.headline: Duke turns defense into offense again with another fast break dunk
